{"comments":"Gizmo Geometry — Visual representation of transform handles.\n\n## Design\nGenerates the 3D geometry for translate/rotate/scale gizmos.\nEach axis is a separate piece for independent hit testing.\n\n## Color Convention (Three.js/3D graphics standard)\n- X axis: Red   (RGB 1, 0, 0)\n- Y axis: Green (RGB 0, 1, 0)\n- Z axis: Blue  (RGB 0, 0, 1)\n\n## Geometry Types\n- Translate: Arrow (cone + cylinder) per axis, plane squares\n- Rotate: Torus ring per axis\n- Scale: Cube handle per axis, center cube for uniform\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[81,3]},"title":"TranslateArrowX"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[82,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[82,3]},"title":"TranslateArrowY"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[83,3]},"title":"TranslateArrowZ"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[84,3]},"title":"TranslatePlaneXY"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[85,3]},"title":"TranslatePlaneXZ"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[86,3]},"title":"TranslatePlaneYZ"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/GizmoGeometry.purs","start":[88,3]},"t